WEBVTT

00:00.984 --> 00:03.653
<i>Previously on Transformers Prime:</i>

00:03.940 --> 00:06.150
If you don't survive, Optimus,

00:06.320 --> 00:08.320
I fear neither will this planet!

00:08.320 --> 00:09.820
No!!!

00:09.990 --> 00:10.780
What happened?

00:10.870 --> 00:12.070
Wasn't me.

00:12.120 --> 00:12.870
Me neither.

00:12.910 --> 00:14.200
<i>I happened!</i>

00:14.450 --> 00:16.160
Optimus! Our past alliances —

00:17.080 --> 00:18.920
Autobot, Decepticon — no longer matter,

00:20.790 --> 00:22.880
not while Unicron lives.

00:23.210 --> 00:26.300
I can lead you directly into Unicron's Spark.

00:26.380 --> 00:28.760
A truce between Autobot and Decepticon...

00:29.720 --> 00:32.390
Optimus!
How are we supposed to stop Unicron?

00:32.509 --> 00:34.640
With a Matrix of Leadership.

00:34.720 --> 00:37.520
It appears our Leader
has abandoned us.

00:37.680 --> 00:40.150
I believe we must consider
the possibility of a future

00:40.850 --> 00:43.190
without Megatron.

00:43.230 --> 00:48.450
Jack... I feel you have earned the responsibility
of safeguarding this important device.

00:48.740 --> 00:51.070
Until I return.

00:51.070 --> 00:53.240
So... how long before Unicron
knows we're here?

00:54.290 --> 00:58.000
Make no mistake...
he already does.

01:02.861 --> 01:04.456
Argh!

